window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>COMPLETE SERIES</b></p> <p>Sophie's in 19th century London. Even as she frantically searches for the artefact that can grant her safe passage to her daughter, the Roman god Janus is tearing up the fabric of time to hunt her down. He knows that for Sophie to be reunited with her child, he must die.</p> <p>Freddy, Hugo, and Charlotte are by Sophie's side but the odds are impossible, their doom inevitable.</p> <p>How do you cheat fate?</p> <p><i>Endgame</i> is the sixth and last book of the first Shorten Chronicles series. Devour this thrilling romantic adventure and relish the heart-stopping climax. You won’t want it to end.</p>"; 
